text: <!channel> anyone knows of a good place online to buy expensive tires and tubes (hopefully with a discount)? Amazon doesn't seem to have a good selection.
i've purchased stuff from <http://www.nashbar.com/> in the past - theyve got pretty good prices
not sure how their prices compare, but I've always liked Harris Cyclery <http://harriscyclery.net/>

attachments.text: Harris Cyclery. We ship bicycle parts and accessories worldwide. We sell Giant Bicycles, Brooks saddles, Brompton folding bicycles and Busch & Müller dynamo lighting.
